metadata.name: On Chain Death #1
metadata.description: On Chain Death is an expansion of the Paper Chasers community focused on a popular character trait known as The Death Rider. Death ain't all about reaping souls, Death likes ice cream, parrots, pizza and beer too. Death likes to party!                                                                        *Allowlist Access is limited to OCK and Paper Chasers holders:          Price : FREE (Max. 1 per wallet) - Public Price : 0.013 ETH (Max. 10 per wallet) - Mint Date : 11/20/2022
